  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "8 more are wanted for MP Amarakirthi's murder",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The CCTV footage of the killing of the Member of Parliament Mr. Amarakirthi Athukorala and three persons including his security police sergeant in Nittambuwa town on May 9th. The police are seeking public assistance to arrest 8 more persons identified through the footage.",
        "The police are publishing the photographs of the eight persons and asking the public to provide information about them to the Homicide and Organized Crime Investigation Division on 0112514217 (Director) or 0718592868 (Assistant Director).",
        "Regarding this incident, 35 suspects have been arrested and most of them have been arrested on CCTV. The police media division further says that they have been identified through the footage."
      ],
